[I] Portable OpenBSD ksh, based on the Public Domain KornShell

[T] Unlike other ports of OpenBSD ksh, this port is entirely self-contained and
[T] aims to be maximally portable across operating systems and C compilers. We
[T] are always looking for new combinations to add support for.

[U] https://github.com/ibara/oksh

